{"tid":2436851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[預言] 2022 年立法會熱血公民鄭松泰成功入閘","createTime":"2021-03-07T12:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T13:15:09.000Z","uid":354974,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e284d8ea01bcfeea47a390b8e721620bcbe422a","tid":2436851,"uid":354974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，全力狙擊熱狗既時候到啦！"},{"pid":"e6b510750452215c126211d2e75345bff138da0f","tid":2436851,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b398d9ef7770dd4bbf39acedb22804a93cb733aa","tid":2436851,"uid":354974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"大公文匯新聞<br />\n要聞<br />\n呵呵，4年了，他終於道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉<br />\n2020.07.28 19:30:00<br />\n香港立法會選舉提名期將於7月31日結束，包括黃之鋒在內的多名反對派參選人陸續收到選舉主任來信。其中，香港新界西地方選區選舉主任黃展翹昨日(27日)致信「港獨」組織「熱血公民」主席、立法會議員鄭松泰，重提其四年前倒插國旗一事。<br />\n<br />\n黃展翹質疑，鄭松泰如何顯示他忠誠接受和履行擁護《基本法》，以及效忠中華人民共和國香港特別行政區的承諾。信中要求其在7月28日中午12點前回復上述問題。<br />\n<br />\n據觀察者網報道，今日(28日)中午，鄭松泰在其臉書賬號作出回應，一改過去言行，就自己2016年在立法會議事廳倒插國旗一事致歉。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰聲稱，經過這些年的觀察和反省，他認為當年所做之事的表達方式確實不對，「但由於政府及公眾再無問及事件，無法表達對國家和基本法的敬意」，因此借今次回信表達歉意，並承諾改過遷善。<br />\n<br />\n他還宣稱，會繼續擁護《基本法》，愛護國旗和區旗，並申明自己絕不支持「香港獨立」的主張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tkww.hk/a/202007/28/AP5f200c60e4b065606a53e411.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tkww.hk%2Fa%2F202007%2F28%2FAP5f200c60e4b065606a53e411.html&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d1e88421\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tkww.hk/a/202007/28/AP5f200c60e4b065606a53e411.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7e73e956aa601ac986210bb3a9526755c1feb02","tid":2436851,"uid":354974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"立此存照！"},{"pid":"24fbd1cfa7b661ab71179738cd0db14ce6967379","tid":2436851,"uid":178188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"直接委任啦重選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bec0e569fa7e04f6561f4901f17eef7ee02b58e","tid":2436851,"uid":354974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24fbd1cfa7b661ab71179738cd0db14ce6967379","tid":2436851,"uid":178188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"直接委任啦重選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T13:15:09.000Z","msg":"共產黨就係要有選舉搵人做政治花瓶<br />\n咁先可以自圓其說，香港有民主選舉"}]}